des:
This audio goes from 20 Hertz down to 3 Hertz, over 30 minutes. 
 \
Say Alexa stop, to quiet the sound. 
 \
Say Alexa, exit to quit. 
 After 30 minutes, ocean waves will play." 
 \
In the absence of stereo headphones, concentrate on the flutter and it will work equally well.
